  "title": "(IMMEDIATE) TRAINEE EVENTS CREW (mentorship provided!)",
  "description": "<p><strong>✨TRAINEE EVENTS CREW ( NO EXPERIENCE NEEDED )✨</strong><br />At our core, we believe in being good to each othe, being good to ourselves, and having fun while doing great work. If you enjoy a fast-paced, innovative, and collaborative environment, you’ll fit right in 🚀<br /></p><p>You’ll support our client in reaching their target audience through meaningful conversations, impactful events, and smart solutions recommendations. 🎯<br /></p><p>🔥 What you’ll be doing <br />💡 Recommend training and learning solutions that suit customer needs.<br />🎪 Represent our client at corporate events, roadshows, class visits and seminars.<br />🫂 Lead and guide a team of consultants during assigned events.<br />📞 Follow up on sales leads & collect feedback to improve customer experience.<br /></p><p>🌟 About you <br />📚 You have a strong learning attitude and love self-improvement <br />💪🏻 You take pride in your hard work and consistency <br />🤝 You show emotional intelligence in conversations whether with customers or your team <br />🚀 You’re a self starter who’s eager to grow, learn, and excel<br /></p><p>🎉No experience? No problem! <br />We welcome individuals from all backgrounds - your attitude matters more than your past experience. If you’re ready to grow in a dynamic environment…<br /></p><p>👉🏻 <em><strong>APPLY NOW </strong></em>and build your career with us! 💫</p>",
